response.original_title: PAW Patrol Marshall And Chase On The Case
response.overview: Chase is on the case and Marshall is all fired up for these 8 PAW Patrol adventures! Join the team as their police pup and firedog lead them on some "ruff-ruff" rescues.  Marshall and Chase on the Case! is the third DVD release of PAW Patrol. It was released in the United States on March 3, 2015, in Australia on June 24, 2015, in New Zealand on July 1, 2015 and in the United Kingdom on July 27, 2015.
